# uv lockfile — dev/CI resolves fresh via `uv sync`; not tracked (matches the core repo).
# Distribution is via the built wheel, whose deps come from pyproject.toml, so consumers
# never see this file. Commit it deliberately (with CI `uv sync --frozen`) if you later
# want pinned/reproducible dev environments.
/bindings/python/uv.lock
